                    <span>This book travels almost everywhere with me, along with Colin Moock's ASDG2.  Where ASDG2 stops Joey Lott picks up the pieces and assembles them into practical and useful examples that can be directly applied to everyday projects.<p>The Actionscript Cookbook should be a part of any developers library.  Joey Lott's books consistently impress me as I've also found the Complete Flash Remoting to be invaluable to have around.</span>
                  
              
